    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-5">
      Clear marketing that actually works.
    </h1>

    <p class="text-lg text-[#dae4eb] mb-7 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      Strategy, content, and creative work designed to help small businesses grow without wasted effort.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
      <button onclick="scrollToSection('strategy')" class="px-8 py-3 border border-white">
