        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-[#e6dfd7] rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="mb-3">Long-term growth</h3>
        <p class="text-[#8a8175] text-sm">
          Content and SEO that build authority and steady traffic over time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-[#e6dfd7] rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="mb-3">Engagement & brand</h3>
        <p class="text-[#8a8175] text-sm">
          Social media and creative direction for visibility and consistency.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-[#e6dfd7] rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="mb-3">Local & traditional</h3>
        <p class="text-[#8a8175] text-sm">
