        <h3 class="mb-3">Word-of-mouth</h3>
        <p class="text-[#8a8175] text-sm">
          Events and PR to build trust and real-world momentum.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-[#e6dfd7] rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="mb-3">Mobile-first</h3>
        <p class="text-[#8a8175] text-sm">
          SMS and high-attention messaging for timely communication.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- STATEMENT -->
    <div class="mt-12 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p class="italic text-[#5f5a52] mb-4">
        “The key is finding the mix that aligns with your audience and goals.”
      </p>

      <p class="text-[#8a8175]">
        I help you focus on the 1–3 channels that matter most, then test and build from there.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
